question.title: java.lang.UnsatisfiedLinkError: Unable to load library 'tesseract':
question.body:
Hey i am trying to use tess4j for tesseract and having this issue for intelliJ on Mac. Tesseract is working when I use terminal but whenever I use tess4J, it throws me this error :

Exception in thread "JavaFX Application Thread" java.lang.UnsatisfiedLinkError: Unable to load library 'tesseract': dlopen(libtesseract.dylib, 0x0009): tried: 'libtesseract.dylib' (no such file), '/System/Volumes/Preboot/Cryptexes/OSlibtesseract.dylib' (no such file),

Thanks for your help
